275
00:13:21,206 --> 00:13:22,581
Didn't want to talk
on the phone,

276
00:13:22,669 --> 00:13:25,106
but he implied
he had a story to tell.

277
00:13:25,463 --> 00:13:28,876
Well, that's a beginning.

278
00:13:30,837 --> 00:13:32,976
Uh, I remember we watched

