00:13:48,407 --> 00:13:50,496
Gold medal. Gold shoes.

285
00:13:50,724 --> 00:13:52,788
We laughed about it a lot.

286
00:13:52,987 --> 00:13:55,937
And then, uh, an hour later,

287
00:13:56,025 --> 00:13:57,897
I was standing in the shower,

288
00:13:58,742 --> 00:14:00,358
my face to the wall,

289
00:14:02,361 --> 00:14:05,085
wishing that I had
these golden shoes,

290
00:14:05,173 --> 00:14:09,187
wishing that I had these shoes
so that I could run away.

291
00:14:10,972 --> 00:14:12,663
Plus, I heard that

292
00:14:13,565 --> 00:14:15,176
he was working with kids again.

293
00:14:16,124 --> 00:14:17,546
Mr. Raposa,

294
00:14:18,741 --> 00:14:21,155
given everything
you've described,

295
00:14:21,467 --> 00:14:24,122
everything you testified to,

296
00:14:24,733 --> 00:14:27,858
why'd you keep it all
to yourself all these years?

297
00:14:28,298 --> 00:14:29,577
If that man

298
00:14:29,665 --> 00:14:32,804
did all the terrible things
you just testified to,

299
00:14:33,242 --> 00:14:34,577
why not expose him?

300
00:14:34,670 --> 00:14:36,280
My brother Ryan tried.

301
00:14:36,903 --> 00:14:40,710
He told the truth over and over.
