302
00:14:40,798 --> 00:14:42,546
He went to anybody
who would listen,

303
00:14:42,634 --> 00:14:43,898
and a lot of people
who wouldn't,

304
00:14:43,985 --> 00:14:47,030
but nothing changed,
and it ruined his life.

305
00:14:47,118 --> 00:14:49,999
So if you didn't
talk to anybody,

306
00:14:50,429 --> 00:14:54,129
didn't go the authorities,
didn't seek out therapy,

307
00:14:54,497 --> 00:14:55,759
what did you do?

308
00:14:56,249 --> 00:14:58,663
I handled it in my own way,
I guess.

309
00:14:58,966 --> 00:15:01,403
I bulked up, I joined the army
right out of high school.

310
00:15:01,490 --> 00:15:03,851
I-I figured if I could
make myself a-a tough guy,

311
00:15:03,939 --> 00:15:07,101
nobody would
ever take advantage of me again.

312
00:15:07,489 --> 00:15:09,733
I got out of the service, I...

313
00:15:12,663 --> 00:15:15,608
married a wonderful woman,
bought a little house.

314
00:15:16,533 --> 00:15:19,449
I was determined
