00:20:05,723 --> 00:20:06,893
Eventually.

426
00:20:06,980 --> 00:20:08,329
How'd you feel about that?

427
00:20:08,416 --> 00:20:09,983
Thought I'd died
and gone to heaven.

428
00:20:13,278 --> 00:20:14,887
My dad was in jail.

429
00:20:15,466 --> 00:20:18,737
I lived with my aunt...
Who, between us,

430
00:20:18,825 --> 00:20:21,434
had her own issues with drugs.

431
00:20:22,212 --> 00:20:26,409
Truth is, I remember thinking,
"This is pretty good."

432
00:20:26,497 --> 00:20:27,609
Okay.

433
00:20:27,696 --> 00:20:31,918
Let's go back to the time you
spent alone with Mr. Maybrook.

434
00:20:32,177 --> 00:20:33,571
Did he touch you?

