00:32:29,901 --> 00:32:32,128
She would invite them
up to the house.

696
00:32:32,818 --> 00:32:34,995
Didn't Marissa reach out
to her before the trial?

697
00:32:35,141 --> 00:32:37,169
Yeah. She worked
with him for years.

698
00:32:37,257 --> 00:32:38,955
Apparently she just loved him.

699
00:32:39,042 --> 00:32:41,537
But if that's the case,
why isn't the defense

700
00:32:41,625 --> 00:32:42,610
putting her on the stand?

701
00:32:47,250 --> 00:32:48,828
Can I help you?

702
00:32:49,133 --> 00:32:53,203
Yes. I'm looking for Mrs.
Helms. Mrs. Lydia Helms.

