00:32:54,492 --> 00:32:55,623
I'm Dr. Jason Bull.

705
00:32:55,710 --> 00:32:57,625
I'm representing
Mr. Stephen Raposa

706
00:32:57,712 --> 00:32:59,695
in a civil suit against
Peter Maybrook,

707
00:32:59,783 --> 00:33:01,089
who I believe
you worked for.

708
00:33:02,047 --> 00:33:04,067
You know, I've already
had this conversation

709
00:33:04,154 --> 00:33:05,844
with a woman from your office.

710
00:33:06,508 --> 00:33:09,903
As I explained to her,
I really have nothing to say.

711
00:33:10,610 --> 00:33:11,656
Right.

712
00:33:13,445 --> 00:33:15,586
Aren't you worried
he's gonna do it again?

713
00:33:19,172 --> 00:33:20,953
I'd be grateful
if you'd invite me in.

714
00:33:21,040 --> 00:33:22,938
I'll only need ten
minutes of your time.

715
00:33:23,042 --> 00:33:26,953
Save us both the trouble of
me having to subpoena you.

716
00:33:27,155 --> 00:33:28,286
The truth is,

717
00:33:28,374 --> 00:33:30,320
I don't know anything.

718
00:33:30,634 --> 00:33:33,289
Not for certain, not that
I'd swear to in court.

719
00:33:33,586 --> 00:33:34,844
But you suspected
something.

720
00:33:35,059 --> 00:33:36,758
Not until that last summer.

721
00:33:37,017 --> 00:33:38,914
Peter decided
to close the camp.

722
00:33:39,885 --> 00:33:42,352
Anyway, we-we were
selling the estate,

723
00:33:42,440 --> 00:33:44,524
and I was helping
to prepare for the move.

724
00:33:45,469 --> 00:33:47,196
Peter was
an avid photographer,

725
00:33:47,284 --> 00:33:48,842
and I knew he loved
his darkroom,

726
00:33:48,930 --> 00:33:52,336
so I decided I would just
pack it myself.

727
00:33:53,438 --> 00:33:56,235
And did you see something
in the darkroom?

728
00:33:57,016 --> 00:33:58,492
Not what you think.

729
00:33:59,339 --> 00:34:00,875
Nothing lewd.

730
00:34:01,646 --> 00:34:05,711
Just... pictures of boys.

731
00:34:07,347 --> 00:34:08,578
