732
00:34:09,313 --> 00:34:11,719
And taken with
such affection.

733
00:34:12,977 --> 00:34:16,506
He made them all look beautiful,
like-like an artist

734
00:34:16,594 --> 00:34:19,272
when he paints his lover
or his muse.

735
00:34:20,164 --> 00:34:21,899
It was like he was
trying to

736
00:34:22,305 --> 00:34:25,391
desperately capture something,
hold onto something.

737
00:34:27,515 --> 00:34:29,455
It felt intensely private.

738
00:34:33,125 --> 00:34:34,133
Hello.

739
00:34:34,300 --> 00:34:35,990
Stephen, am I catching you
at dinner?

740
00:34:36,078 --> 00:34:38,238
It's Jason Bull.
There's something I'd like to ask you.

741
00:34:38,328 --> 00:34:39,516
Sure.

742
00:34:39,604 --> 00:34:42,512
Do you remember Maybrook
ever taking photos of you,

743
00:34:42,600 --> 00:34:44,602
or maybe the two
of you together?

744
00:34:44,789 --> 00:34:47,953
Uh, no. I remember hearing
he had a darkroom,

745
00:34:48,040 --> 00:34:50,173
but I don't remember him
taking pictures. Why?

746
00:34:50,461 --> 00:34:53,176
Did Ryan ever talk about
Maybrook taking pictures?

747
00:34:53,328 --> 00:34:54,779
Ryan talked about
a lot of things

748
00:34:54,867 --> 00:34:55,830
when it came to Maybrook.

749
00:34:55,917 --> 00:34:57,891
Mostly I tried to tune him out.

750
00:34:58,067 --> 00:35:00,965
But I do remember the night
he ransacked Maybrook's place.

751
00:35:01,053 --> 00:35:03,141
He brought back
three or four cameras.

752
00:35:03,781 --> 00:35:06,015
I figured he probably wanted
to sell them for drug money,

753
00:35:06,102 --> 00:35:08,017
so I took them, hid them.

754
00:35:08,281 --> 00:35:10,019
I didn't want him
getting caught.

755
00:35:10,106 --> 00:35:11,703
Getting in more trouble.

756
00:35:12,164 --> 00:35:13,477
You took them.

757
00:35:13,588 --> 00:35:15,633
Any chance you still have 'em?

758
00:35:18,196 --> 00:35:20,896
Your Honor, in light
of some new evidence

759
00:35:20,984 --> 00:35:23,139
that's just been brought
to our attention,

760
00:35:23,227 --> 00:35:24,880
the plaintiff would like
to recall

761
00:35:24,967 --> 00:35:26,727
Peter Maybrook to the stand.

762
00:35:31,149 --> 00:35:34,334
Mr. Maybrook, now, I understand

763
00:35:34,422 --> 00:35:36,688
you have an interest
in photography.

764
00:35:36,892 --> 00:35:38,329
I do.Ah.

765
00:35:39,977 --> 00:35:41,854
Do you recognize this camera?

766
00:35:42,086 --> 00:35:44,639
I believe it belonged
to you at one time.

767
00:35:44,930 --> 00:35:47,294
I-I have no idea.

768
00:35:47,381 --> 00:35:50,341
I-I may have had
a camera like that in the past.

769
00:35:50,953 --> 00:35:53,305
Oh, well,

770
00:35:53,400 --> 00:35:56,904
w-would it surprise you to learn

771
00:35:56,992 --> 00:35:59,828
that your fingerprints
were found on this camera?

772
00:36:00,070 --> 00:36:03,170
Or that we contacted
the manufacturer

773
00:36:03,258 --> 00:36:06,547
and learned that
you sent a warranty card

774
00:36:06,738 --> 00:36:11,117
for a camera with the exact
same serial numbers as this one?

775
00:36:11,746 --> 00:36:14,578
It seems like it might have
been my camera.Ah.

776
00:36:14,666 --> 00:36:16,117
Ha-ha, well,

777
00:36:16,308 --> 00:36:18,719
I appreciate you
conceding that, sir.

778
00:36:19,201 --> 00:36:20,922
See, but here's the thing.

779
00:36:22,027 --> 00:36:25,711
Did you know
the reason we found this camera...

780
00:36:26,477 --> 00:36:29,219
the reason I am able
to show it to you here today

781
00:36:29,423 --> 00:36:33,993
is because Ryan Raposa,
my client's late brother,

782
00:36:34,218 --> 00:36:35,547
stole it from you?

783
00:36:37,438 --> 00:36:38,903
You remember that?

784
00:36:39,383 --> 00:36:42,625
About ten years ago,
your home was burglarized.

785
00:36:43,477 --> 00:36:46,136
I believe, along with
everything else,

786
00:36:46,223 --> 00:36:48,156
four cameras were taken.

787
00:36:48,559 --> 00:36:52,047
Did you know that
Ryan was the thief?

788
00:36:53,026 --> 00:36:56,029
Turns out he was...
he was very angry with you.

789
00:36:56,232 --> 00:36:58,242
Even after all these years.

790
00:36:59,320 --> 00:37:01,789
See, I'm guessing
you never knew.

791
00:37:01,984 --> 00:37:03,588
I'm guessing you never
told the police

792
00:37:03,675 --> 00:37:06,359
because you were afraid
of what they might find here.

793
00:37:06,808 --> 00:37:08,437
Turns out it's been
in my client's basement

794
00:37:08,524 --> 00:37:09,333
this whole time.

795
00:37:09,469 --> 00:37:11,204
Objection. Relevance.

796
00:37:11,291 --> 00:37:13,906
I don't see what this has
to do with anything.

797
00:37:14,120 --> 00:37:16,949
Your Honor,
if you will permit me,

798
00:37:17,036 --> 00:37:19,169
I assure you that
I will prove to the court

799
00:37:19,256 --> 00:37:20,664
just how relevant
this camera is.

800
00:37:20,752 --> 00:37:21,961
Go ahead.

801
00:37:22,049 --> 00:37:26,172
To make things easier
for everyone to see,

802
00:37:26,408 --> 00:37:30,455
I'm gonna connect this camera
to this computer,

803
00:37:30,643 --> 00:37:34,477
and broadcast the images

804
00:37:34,891 --> 00:37:38,536
to the monitor
right next to Mr. Maybrook.

805
00:37:38,766 --> 00:37:41,750
Hey, is that you in the photo
there, Mr. Maybrook?

806
00:37:42,445 --> 00:37:44,396
Ten or so years ago,
yes.

807
00:37:44,484 --> 00:37:45,906
Ah.

808
00:37:45,994 --> 00:37:47,969
What about this photo?

809
00:37:49,895 --> 00:37:50,896
Hmm?

810
00:37:51,305 --> 00:37:53,203
Now, what was going on there?

811
00:37:54,024 --> 00:37:55,883
You set up a timer
or something?

812
00:37:58,219 --> 00:37:59,818
Ah, that's okay.

813
00:38:00,539 --> 00:38:02,078
That's all right.

814
00:38:02,503 --> 00:38:03,908
I was just trying to figure out

815
00:38:03,996 --> 00:38:05,867
if there was a third person
in the room.

816
00:38:06,815 --> 00:38:08,828
That's not important, right?

817
00:38:09,088 --> 00:38:12,209
What is important is that
we all agree that

818
00:38:12,297 --> 00:38:14,774
that is you in the photo.

819
00:38:15,312 --> 00:38:17,107
On the left-hand side
of the frame

820
00:38:17,195 --> 00:38:20,305
with your shirt off
and your arms around...

821
00:38:21,369 --> 00:38:23,197
We'll get to him in a minute.

822
00:38:23,425 --> 00:38:24,774
That you, sir?

823
00:38:26,246 --> 00:38:27,646
It seems to be.

824
00:38:27,734 --> 00:38:30,602
I'm sorry, I need a yes or no.

825
00:38:30,849 --> 00:38:32,198
Mr. Maybrook?

826
00:38:34,085 --> 00:38:35,086
Yes.

827
00:38:36,063 --> 00:38:38,188
What about the boy
in this photo?

828
00:38:39,641 --> 00:38:41,359
That boy right there.

829
00:38:42,062 --> 00:38:44,149
He must be about 13.

830
00:38:44,680 --> 00:38:46,287
He has his shirt off, too,

831
00:38:46,375 --> 00:38:47,909
and you two are
holding each other.

832
00:38:48,148 --> 00:38:50,008
You happen to remember
his name?

833
00:38:52,258 --> 00:38:53,938
I'm not sure.

834
00:38:55,515 --> 00:38:58,453
Roberto... Renaldo...

835
00:38:59,834 --> 00:39:01,102
I'm not sure.

836
00:39:01,396 --> 00:39:02,832
Eh, you're not sure.

837
00:39:03,051 --> 00:39:06,142
That's all right,
that's all right, Mr. Maybrook.

838
00:39:06,363 --> 00:39:07,799
What about this photo?

839
00:39:07,886 --> 00:39:10,105
That you?

840
00:39:10,296 --> 00:39:11,625
In the picture?

841
00:39:12,476 --> 00:39:15,914
Let the record reflect that
I have just shown the defendant

842
00:39:16,031 --> 00:39:19,376
a photo of himself naked

843
00:39:19,891 --> 00:39:22,641
in a bathroom with a minor!

844
00:39:25,512 --> 00:39:27,555
Actually, I'm not certain
that is me.

845
00:39:28,227 --> 00:39:29,570
Yeah?

846
00:39:29,831 --> 00:39:32,969
Hey, let me remind you that
you are still under oath.

847
00:39:33,519 --> 00:39:35,434
I'd also like you to know
that I've got

848
00:39:35,522 --> 00:39:38,508
33 more images
very much like this one,

849
00:39:38,633 --> 00:39:41,311
and I am happy to show the court
all of them,

850
00:39:41,398 --> 00:39:44,009
and ask you to identify yourself
on each and every one.

851
00:39:44,096 --> 00:39:47,317
Or you can concede that
that is you,

852
00:39:47,483 --> 00:39:49,758
and for the moment,
the slide show is over.

853
00:39:50,415 --> 00:39:51,720
Your choice.

854
00:39:57,405 --> 00:39:59,086
Actually, uh...

855
00:40:00,417 --> 00:40:02,172
on reflection...

856
00:40:05,204 --> 00:40:06,930
...I believe that is me.

857
00:40:13,563 --> 00:40:14,945
Oh, God.

858
00:40:15,345 --> 00:40:17,234
Bull, tell Stephen he did it.

859
00:40:17,827 --> 00:40:19,652
I think he knows, Marissa.

860
00:40:20,102 --> 00:40:21,699
I think he knows.

861
00:40:28,111 --> 00:40:29,664
You think he's happy?

862
00:40:29,906 --> 00:40:32,534
I didn't know him,
other than what you told me.

863
00:40:32,622 --> 00:40:36,495
But you picked a beautiful spot
for his ashes.

864
00:40:38,672 --> 00:40:40,457
$35 million.

865
00:40:40,805 --> 00:40:42,896
You think it-it even
matters to him?

866
00:40:42,984 --> 00:40:44,287
To Maybrook?

867
00:40:44,524 --> 00:40:47,028
Obviously, I'm going
to donate it.

868
00:40:47,115 --> 00:40:48,334
I don't know to whom
just yet.

869
00:40:48,421 --> 00:40:50,771
Some worthy cause.

870
00:40:57,996 --> 00:40:59,930
I know it's supposed
to make me feel better.

871
00:41:00,024 --> 00:41:01,956
I know it's his punishment,
but I swear to you,

872
00:41:02,043 --> 00:41:04,641
the whole time that we were
sitting there in court,

873
00:41:05,743 --> 00:41:07,570
money never crossed my mind.

874
00:41:07,790 --> 00:41:10,053
I think I somehow
convinced myself that

875
00:41:10,210 --> 00:41:12,180
they'd do something to him.

876
00:41:12,525 --> 00:41:14,609
Not just take
some of his money.

877
00:41:15,042 --> 00:41:17,915
I'm pretty sure Ryan's
in heaven rolling his eyes.

878
00:41:18,773 --> 00:41:21,228
Okay, if you are done
feeling sorry for yourself

879
00:41:21,323 --> 00:41:23,804
because all you got was
$35 million you never wanted,

880
00:41:23,891 --> 00:41:25,763
I think I have
some good news for you.

881
00:41:26,266 --> 00:41:27,758
What? What is it?

882
00:41:28,031 --> 00:41:30,347
Peter Maybrook was
just arrested.

883
00:41:34,903 --> 00:41:36,514
But how?
How is that possible?

884
00:41:36,602 --> 00:41:38,952
The statute of limitations
on criminal charges...

885
00:41:39,040 --> 00:41:40,260
I didn't want you
to get your hopes up,

886
00:41:40,347 --> 00:41:42,219
but Bull had a strong hunch
that if Maybrook had

887
00:41:42,306 --> 00:41:44,576
taken pictures of himself
with underage boys in the past,

888
00:41:44,664 --> 00:41:46,000
he probably took pictures
of himself

889
00:41:46,087 --> 00:41:48,024
with underage boys
in the present.

890
00:41:48,125 --> 00:41:50,744
So Danny worked with
an old NYPD colleague

891
00:41:50,831 --> 00:41:52,820
to drum up probable cause,

892
00:41:53,055 --> 00:41:54,661
and they raided his office
this morning.

893
00:41:54,748 --> 00:41:55,664
Bull was right.

894
00:41:55,752 --> 00:41:57,992
Maybrook is going away
for life.

895
00:42:01,031 --> 00:42:03,609
You think maybe Ryan's done
with his eye-rolling?

896
00:42:06,137 --> 00:42:07,633
Yeah, I think so.

897
00:42:09,503 --> 00:42:10,836
Thank you.

